name: Breach
content:
"Breach" was the callsign of a First Order TIE/se Bomber pilot and ordnance expert. "Breach" once executed an attack run against an MG-100 StarFortress SF-17.
"Breach" was created for the miniatures game Star Wars: X-Wing Second Edition in the card of the same name released in the 2021 Fury of the First Order Squadron Pack.
